  { q: 'How much does AC installation cost in Wesley Chapel?', a: 'A complete AC installation in Wesley Chapel typically runs $5,500 to $12,000 for central systems (like-for-like changeout through mid-efficiency 16 to 18 SEER2), $11,000 to $16,000 for high-efficiency variable-speed systems, and $3,800 to $6,800 for a single-zone mini-split. Every quote includes Manual-J load calculation, Pasco County permitting, first-year tune-up, and warranty registration. See our AC replacement page for the full pricing table.' },
  { q: 'Which Wesley Chapel neighborhoods do you install in?', a: 'All of them, including Epperson, Mirada, Watergrass, Persimmon Park, Seven Oaks, Meadow Pointe, Lexington Oaks, Wiregrass Ranch, Estancia, Chapel Pines, Saddlebrook, Quail Hollow, Country Walk, and New River. We coordinate HOA equipment-placement approval where required.' },
  { q: 'Do you handle Pasco County permits for Wesley Chapel installs?', a: 'Yes. Every install includes the Pasco County mechanical permit, the final inspection, and any HOA approval coordination. Florida license CAC1816515. You never deal with the county directly.' },
  { q: 'What SEER2 rating should I get for a Wesley Chapel home?', a: 'The 2026 Florida minimum is 15.2 SEER2. The sweet spot for most Wesley Chapel homes is 16 to 18 SEER2. Variable-speed 20+ SEER2 systems make sense for homes over 2,500 sq ft, allergy-sensitive families, or anyone planning to stay 10+ years. We do the efficiency math on your proposal.' },
  { q: 'How long does AC installation take in Wesley Chapel?', a: 'A standard same-tonnage changeout is one day, usually 7 to 9 hours. Projects with ductwork replacement, line-set upgrades, or electrical service changes can run 1 to 2 days. Permit and inspection handling is included.' },
  { q: 'Do I need a new AC or can I repair the old one?', a: 'Apply the $5,000 rule: multiply the age of the system by the estimated repair cost. Over $5,000 means replacement usually wins. A 12-year-old system with a $500 compressor repair = $6,000, replace. A 6-year-old system with the same repair = $3,000, fix it. Our AC replacement page walks through the full math.' },
  { q: 'Do you offer financing?', a: 'Yes. Synchrony financing with 0% introductory rates and terms up to 120 months on qualifying installs. Many Wesley Chapel homeowners find the monthly payment comes in below what they save on their electric bill after upgrading.' },
];

