---
<ServiceLayout
  slug="ac-installation-wesley-chapel"
  title="AC Installation Wesley Chapel | Free Quote · 0% Financing"
  description="Wesley Chapel AC installation - Manual-J sized, permitted, warrantied. Carrier, Trane, Rheem. Free quote + 0% financing. 4.9★ · 700+ reviews. Call (813) 395-2324."
  h1="AC Installation in Wesley Chapel & Tampa Bay, FL"
  eyebrow="AC Installation · Wesley Chapel"
  subtitle={`A new AC system is one of the biggest home investments you'll make in the Wesley Chapel climate. We size it right with a full <span class="text-accent-400 font-semibold">Manual-J load calculation</span>, install to manufacturer spec, and stand behind the work with a 2-year installation warranty.`}
  heroImage="/images/HVAC-Installation-Tampa-Bay-%E2%80%93-New-Outdoor-Condenser-Installation.webp"
  serviceName="AC Installation in Wesley Chapel"
